captions.text: (announcer) You know what time it is...

It's time to spin 
the Wheel of Mythicality!
(Rhett) Rhett becomes a pushy waiter.
Hmmm, just here... trying to order.

Uh, yeah.
Whatd'ya want?

- (loudly) I suggest the salmon!
- I'm having--
(yelling) I suggest the salmon!
I feel very strongly about the salmon!

(normal) Okay you want the salmon. 
How do you want that cooked?

- Insalate--
- (yelling) You want it just a little bit

singed on the outside.
That's just how I like it.
Okay, and to drink!

- Okay! Sparkling water!
- (Link stammers) Insalate?

(normally) yes, sparkling water,
that's my favorite.

- (louder) Okay, alright!
- What's insalate?

- Is that another language?
- And I understand you want

the calamari to start.
Good choice, friend!

Soooo, that's like an... 
opposite of a salad?

We're gonna need this table cleared out.
We've got another couple coming in here.

- (straining) Alright!
- Up-up-up! Nope! Nope! Nope! NOPE!

- No tip for you!
- I'll bring your salmon on to the window,

on roller skates.
That's how you like it.

- (thumping hard on back)
- (stifling laughter)
♪ (music) ♪

[Captioned by Keely: 
GMM Captioning Team]
♪ (music continues) ♪

title: The Pushy Waiter (Wheel of Mythicality - Ep. 6)
